		<title>By: Michael Sundgaard</title>
		<link rel="alternate" href="/index.php/architect/enterprisearchitecture/simple-advice-for-choosing-an-esb/#comment-1133" type="text/html" />

		<author>
			<name>Michael Sundgaard</name>
			
